Being a resolute Network Marketing Company the top priority of Nebula ™ will always be the relationship with its members/associates. We collect information that you would provide directly to us based on the scope of our Nebula™ app. Nebula™, as data controller, when activating and using the Nebula™ Services, how Nebula™ receives, collects and uses this data and how you may opt-out at any time, altogether preventing use of the data shared via the Services. Installation and Use After you install and use the Nebula™ App, Nebula™ will collect, process and retain personal information from you and any devices you may use connected with our application. This information may include the following: Storage, geo-location, telephone access, Your IP address, device manufacturer and type, Data operator, IMEI, connection information, screen resolution, camera, usage statistics and device log. This will help us serve you better. Map & Location Information: Nebula™ app would have the access of Google Maps and Location services to enable you to locate our offices from the app itself and we will have a log of your location so that we can provide you the locations of your marketing network and downline members. Similarly members who have you in their marketing network will be able to track your location. Your location will not be public but will be accessible to your direct upline members only. Contacts Information: If you permit the Nebula™ app to access the address book on your device, we may access and store names and contact information from your address book to enable marketing interactions of the concerned contacts based on their history. We will send marketing SMS, emails and/or call your contacts from your phone book. Your contact book is completely private with us and is only meant for marketing and promotional purposes. Device Information: We may collect information about your mobile device, including, for example, the hardware model, operating system and version, software version, IMEI, unique device identifier, advertising identifiers, serial number, device motion information, device IP address and mobile network information. This info will help us understand the device specific issues and help us resolve errors with more precision. Your device information will remain confidential and private with us. Nebula™may use Push Notification Services to notify you about up-dates and important information. In such cases, your phone number may be part of the notification. This message is sent to the push notification service provider, for delivery to your device. You may, however, at any time-opt out or disable push notifications in the Nebula™app. Nebula™app will upload your personal details and your device information on a secure server. This information stored on our server is never circulated or shared with any third party applications or entities. Please note that Nebula™ or Nebula Companies do not responsibility if a user copies, uploads downline data on a third party app or any other server. Our representative will take you on a 2.5 hour drive to Pattaya, a breathtakingly beautiful beach destination. It is here that you can hit the bars, bask on the beaches, shop till you drop, pamper yourself with a massage and relish mouth-watering Thai cuisine. And what does one say about the nightlife in Pattaya? Well, it is one of the most happening in the world. You can spend the evening at leisure. Though we recommend you see the Alcazar Show, a world-famous cabaret that can give the Lido and Moulin Rouge a run for their money. Featuring a grand theatre with 1,200 seats and a state-of-the-art light and sound system, the Alcazar offers a unique blend of acting, stage design, costumes and glamour. Feel free to connect with our representative to take this optional tour at the best price. Savour a delightful dinner at our suggested restaurant and head to the comfort of your hotel. Return to your hotel for a restful overnight stay.
After a scrumptious breakfast at the hotel, speedboat your way to the idyllic Coral Island (KohLan) through the sparkling aqua-blue waters of the Gulf of Thailand. Spend the day under the warm tropical sun - relax, swim, snorkel or just laze around on the island\'s immaculate golden beaches. You can also dive down into the waters to witness the marine life up and close. Lunch is provided after the sightseeing. Recharge yourself with a healthy breakfast at the hotel and embark on a pleasant journey back to Bangkok - the city of temples, spas, endless shopping sprees and a vivid nightlife. Our city tour takes you to some of Bangkok\'s most distinguished Buddhist temples locally known as Wat Wat Pho, Temple of the Reclining Buddha that is home to the largest and the oldest shrine of its kind in Bangkok. Enjoy a shopping spree at the Gems Gallery next in pattaya enroute Bangkok & Reclining Buddha in Bangkok Savour a delightful dinner at our suggested restaurant and head to the comfort of your hotel. Full day is at leisure at Bangkok to explore unlimited shopping opportunities or visit Safari world & Marine Park. Savour a delightful dinner at our suggested restaurant and head to the comfort of your hotel. Post breakfast, c/out and depart for airport to board your flight back home.
